lead_paragraph: Olympic organizers agreed Tuesday to keep the rowing, canoe sprint and swimming venues at their planned sites in Tokyo for the 2020 Games, while postponing a decision until Christmas on a possible switch for volleyball.

headline.print_headline: Rowing, Canoe Sprint, Swimming to Remain at Tokyo Venues
headline.main: Rowing, Canoe Sprint, Swimming to Remain at Tokyo Venues
